#   "message": "Error fetching users and roles"
# }

### =============================================================================
### Testing Scenarios
### =============================================================================

### Scenario 1: Initial Full Sync (All Active Users)
POST {{baseUrl}}?script={{script}}&deploy={{deploy}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "ACTIVE",
  "limit": 1000,
  "offset": 0,
  "includePermissions": true
}

### Scenario 2: Quick Check (Roles Only, No Permissions)
POST {{baseUrl}}?script={{script}}&deploy={{deploy}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "ACTIVE",
  "limit": 1000,
  "includePermissions": false
}

### Scenario 3: Department-Specific Audit (Finance Only)
POST {{baseUrl}}?script={{script}}&deploy={{deploy}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "ACTIVE",
  "department": "Finance",
  "includePermissions": true
}

### Scenario 4: Subsidiary-Specific Audit (US Only)
POST {{baseUrl}}?script={{script}}&deploy={{deploy}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "ACTIVE",
  "subsidiary": "United States",
  "includePermissions": true
}

### Scenario 5: Performance Test (Large Dataset)
POST {{baseUrl}}?script={{script}}&deploy={{deploy}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "ACTIVE",
  "limit": 500,
  "includePermissions": false
}

### =============================================================================
### Pagination Example
### =============================================================================

### Fetch all users with pagination (100 per page)

### Page 1
POST {{baseUrl}}?script={{script}}&deploy={{deploy}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "limit": 100,
  "offset": 0,
  "includePermissions": true
}

### Page 2 (if has_more = true)
POST {{baseUrl}}?script={{script}}&deploy={{deploy}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "limit": 100,
  "offset": 100,
  "includePermissions": true
}

### Page 3 (if has_more = true)
POST {{baseUrl}}?script={{script}}&deploy={{deploy}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "limit": 100,
  "offset": 200,
  "includePermissions": true
}
